al to the company about the company energy xxi is an independent oil and natural gas exploration and production company whose growth strategy emphasizes acquisitions enhanced by its valueadded organic drilling program the companys properties are located in the us gulf of mexico waters and the gulf coast onshore  seymour pierce is energy xxis listing broker in the united kingdom  to learn more visit the energy xxi website at wwwenergyxxicom the energy xxi logo is available at httpwwwglobenewswirecomnewsroomprspkgid contact enquiries of the company energy xxi stewart lawrence vice president investor relations and communications 6 slawrenceenergyxxicom greg smith director investor relations 319 gsmithenergyxxicom seymour pierce nominated adviser jonathan wright corporate broking richard redmayne tel    717 8 pelham bell pottinger james henderson jhendersonpelhambellpottingercouk mark antelme mantelmepelhambellpottingercouk      source energy xxi news provided by acquire media close window  back to top delicious digg facebook linkedin twitter copyright  energy xxi antonio de pinho  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in antonio de pinho chief operating officer and executive vice president exploration and production at energy xxi ltd view full profile are you antonio de pinho claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view antonio de pinhos full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in antonio de pinhos network and community follow changes in antonio de pinhos employment and moneyinmotion connect with antonio de pinho through your network of contacts antonio de pinhos executive work history current chief operating officer and executive vice president exploration and production energy xxi ltd past to view antonio de pinhos complete executive work history sign up now age 5     antonio de pinhos biography antonio de pinho became our chief operating officer on november  1 after be