s of experience in engineering geology operations and management with independent and major oil and gas companies source energy xxi ltd on 116   sign up for equilar atlas and view antonio de pinhos full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like antonio de pinho more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in antonio de pinhos network and community follow changes in antonio de pinhos employment and moneyinmotion connect with antonio de pinho through your network of conections view full profile   search for over 36 executive profiles bio example antonio de pinho antonio de pinhos connections  sign up now to view antonio de pinhos  connections » bruce w busmire chief financial officer energy xxi ltd benjamin marchive former chief operating officer energy xxi ltd scott a griffiths board member energy xxi ltd john d schiller dir president and chief executive officer energy xxi ltd hugh a menown former executive vice president and chief accounting officer energy xxi ltd hill a feinberg chairman and chief executive officer hilltop securities hilltop holdings inc steve nelson former vp drilling and production energy xxi ltd william colvin former board member energy xxi ltd paul davison former board member energy xxi ltd david m dunwoody former board member energy xxi ltd popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith carl g annessa evp and coo hornbeck offshore services inc elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla michael c montgomery board member nmi holdings inc × claim your profile coming soon interested in updating your biography and work history were working on making it happen well email you when this feature is available please enter valid email address done thank you for your interest ok browse executive profiles  a  b  c  d  e  f  g  h  i  j  k  l  m  n  o  p  q  r  s  t 